:45:32.000Z","msg":"這季內容分為：<br />\n1.戒色視頻2個；<br />\n2.戒色文章1篇；<br />\n3.戒色詩歌1首；<br />\n4.戒色圖片158張；<br />\n謝謝大家支持，希望大家早日戒除手淫惡習，找回遺失的美好。你們都是最棒的！<br />\n戒色吧主旨：【婚前禁慾、婚後節制】，既符合傳統文化，又符合中醫養生之道。<br />\n戒色吧走的是科學專業的戒色道路，但也尊重通過信仰來戒除邪淫。<br />\n戒色吧最主要的就是為了幫助大家戒除手淫惡習。<br />\n戒色吧不支持手淫萬病論，因為有很多的致病因素，但手淫導致腎虛，而腎虛百病叢生，這也是不爭的事實。"},{"pid":"a3f05f6ef722ae5fe31e0a837242c21ebfee7d99","tid":507961,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f84385cf068cbc9cadb728f367b9b1225a63ebf","tid":507961,"uid":157584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:45:33.000Z","msg":"Welcome<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a820e327c63bcf608a536e2eca8b7c5cd8fbb8b5","tid":507961,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8617a800eb62a275748ffa63d0376a67736bfda1","tid":507961,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:43:13.000Z","msg":"本人20 擼的已經陽痿早洩了， 很是煩惱 也在戒 請問能陽痿早洩能好嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:46:09.000Z","msg":"死去問林早洩啦屌你老母！"},{"pid":"74a47621c40338898dcc1a73d2058e689bb26824","tid":507961,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"你咪係比人捽lin頭果位臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b5fbeb4cf1f5aee7c371aeec02eed638d42ca929","tid":507961,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:46:25.000Z","msg":"手淫的確會導致身體出現各種傷精的症狀表現，包括身心兩方面的失調，手淫也會影響到一個人的容貌氣質。"},{"pid":"951eeb1ea542270f290e95f095983a94f0e2bd40","tid":507961,"